Actually, I don't think setting `config.root` to the monorepo root `'/Users/pencilcheck/Projects/project-new-expo/apps/expo/'` works; I expect an error like/similar to the one you posted in your other issue.

I'll improve the docs to clarify that.

(Unrelated but I recommend following https://telefunc.com/event-based.)
